<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>My Travel Blog</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #a2d9ff, #fceabb);
    }

    .container {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 50px 20px;
    }

    h1 {
      color: #004e92;
      font-size: 42px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }

    p {
      color: #333;
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Welcome to my <%= title %></h1>
    <h1>Journeys of a Lifetime</h1>
    <p>
      Welcome to my colorful travel blog! Explore breathtaking destinations, cultures, and memories from around the world. 
      From serene beaches to majestic mountains, each place tells a story waiting to be discovered. 
      Here, you’ll find travel tips, hidden gems, and unforgettable experiences from my journeys. 
      Whether you love adventure, culture, or just a peaceful getaway there’s something here for everyone. 
      Pack your bags, grab your camera, and let’s explore the beauty of the world together! Stay tuned for weekly updates and travel inspiration from new destinations.
    </p>
    <img src="/images/beach.png" alt="Beautiful Beach" 
         style="width: 60%; border: 6px solid #004e92; border-radius: 15px; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);">
  </div>
</body>
</html>